[619.0, 353.9, 879.3, 369.7]}, {"text": "$ 173,433", "bbox": [900.4, 354.1, 962.9, 369.7]}, {"text": "$ 202,717", "bbox": [981.6, 354.1, 1044.2, 369.7]}, {"text": "$ 124,193", "bbox": [1062.9, 354.1, 1125.5, 369.7]}, {"text": "(a) In thousands.", "bbox": [619.0, 378.8, 714.8, 392.3]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2011, there was $436 million of total unrec-", "bbox": [637.8, 418.7, 1114.3, 437.4]}, {"text": "ognized compensation cost related to nonvested share- based", "bbox": [619.0, 443.7, 1098.3, 462.4]}, {"text": "compensation grants. This unrecognized compensation is expected", "bbox": [619.0, 468.7, 1142.8, 487.4]}, {"text": "to be recognized over a weighted- average period of two years.", "bbox": [619.0, 493.7, 1100.1, 512.4]}, {"text": "Note 7", "bbox": [847.4, 556.1, 903.3, 574.8]}, {"text": "Pension, Retiree Medical and Savings Plans", "bbox": [643.0, 584.8, 1107.6, 609.8]}, {"text": "Our pension plans cover certain full- time employees in the U.S. and", "bbox": [619.0, 639.5, 1137.2, 658.3]}, {"text": "certain international employees. Benefits are determined based on", "bbox": [619.0, 664.5, 1135.1, 683.3]}, {"text": "either years of service or a combination of years of service and earn-", "bbox": [619.0, 689.5, 1137.6, 708.3]}, {"text": "ings. Certain U.S. and Canada retirees are also eligible for medical", "bbox": [619.0, 714.5, 1121.0, 733.2]}, {"text": "and life insurance benefits (retiree medical) if they meet age and", "bbox": [619.0, 739.5, 1114.9, 758.2]}, {"text": "service requirements. Generally, our share of retiree medical costs is", "bbox": [619.0, 764.5, 1140.7, 783.2]}, {"text": "capped at specified dollar amounts, which vary based upon years of", "bbox": [619.0, 789.5, 1143.8, 808.2]}, {"text": "service, with retirees contributing the remainder of the costs.", "bbox": [619.0, 814.5, 1085.1, 833.2]}, {"text": "Gains and losses resulting from actual experience differing from", "bbox": [637.8, 839.5, 1130.5, 858.2]}, {"text": "our assumptions, including the difference between the actual return", "bbox": [619.0, 864.5, 1146.7, 883.2]}, {"text": "on plan assets and the expected return on plan assets, and from", "bbox": [619.0, 889.5, 1112.9, 908.2]}, {"text": "changes in our assumptions are determined at each measurement", "bbox": [619.0, 914.4, 1130.4, 933.2]}, {"text": "date. If this net accumulated gain or loss exceeds 10% of the greater", "bbox": [619.0, 939.4, 1140.6, 958.2]}, {"text": "of the market- related value of plan assets or plan liabilities, a por-", "bbox": [619.0, 964.4, 1115.6, 983.2]}, {"text": "tion of the net gain or loss is included in expense for the following", "bbox": [619.0, 989.4, 1127.2, 1008.2]}, {"text": "year based upon the average remaining service period of active plan", "bbox": [619.0, 1014.4, 1148.1, 1033.2]}, {"text": "participants, which is approximately 10 years for pension expense", "bbox": [619.0, 1039.4, 1126.0, 1058.2]}, {"text": "and approximately 8 years for retiree medical expense. The cost or", "bbox": [619.0, 1064.4, 1130.2, 1083.2]}, {"text": "benefit of plan changes that increase or decrease benefits for prior", "bbox": [619.0, 1089.4, 1131.9, 1108.2]}, {"text": "employee service (prior service cost/(credit)) is included in earnings", "bbox": [619.0, 1114.4, 1136.9, 1133.1]}, {"text": "on a straight- line basis over the average remaining service period of", "bbox": [619.0, 1139.4, 1141.7, 1158.1]}, {"text": "active plan participants.", "bbox": [619.0, 1164.4, 802.6, 1183.1]}, {"text": "In connection with our acquisitions of PBG and PAS, we assumed", "bbox": [637.8, 1189.4, 1135.5, 1208.1]}, {"text": "sponsorship of pension and retiree medical plans that provide", "bbox": [619.0, 1214.4, 1098.4, 1233.1]}, {"text": "benefits to certain U.S. and international employees. Subsequently,", "bbox": [619.0, 1239.4, 1136.4, 1258.1]}, {"text": "during the third quarter of 2010, we merged the pension plan assets", "bbox": [619.0, 1264.4, 1143.3, 1283.1]}, {"text": "of the legacy PBG and PAS U.S. pension plans with those of PepsiCo", "bbox": [619.0, 1289.4, 1137.3, 1308.1]}, {"text": "into one master trust.", "bbox": [619.0, 1314.3, 783.4, 1333.1]}, {"text": "During 2010, the Compensation Committee of PepsiCo’s Board", "bbox": [637.8, 1339.3, 1121.1, 1358.1]}, {"text": "of Directors approved certain changes to the U.S. pension and", "bbox": [619.0, 1364.3, 1098.0, 1383.1]}, {"text": "retiree medical plans, effective January 1, 2011. Pension plan design", "bbox": [619.0, 1389.3, 1137.8, 1408.1]}, {"text": "changes included implementing a new employer contribution", "bbox": [619.0, 1414.3, 1100.4, 1433.1]}, {"text": "PepsiCo, Inc. 2011 Annual Report", "bbox": [491.1, 1518.9, 715.6, 1535.5]}, {"text": "66", "bbox": [595.2, 1485.9, 611.6, 1501.6]}, {"text": "Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements", "bbox": [62.5, 43.7, 385.6, 60.4]}]}